M

Mat - Class in arma
Mat is a dense matrix with interfaces similar to the Armadillo C++ Algebra Library by Conrad Sanderson et al., based on DenseMatrix64F from Peter Abeles’ Efficient Java Matrix Library (EJML) Version 0.23 - 21.06.2013.

Creates a new matrix by referencing to the provided one.
Mat() - Constructor for class arma.Mat
Creates a new matrix with Mat.n_elem = 0.

Creates a new matrix with the same dimensions and assignments as the provided two-dimensional array.
Mat(int, int) - Constructor for class arma.Mat
Creates a new matrix with Mat.n_rows = numberOfRows and Mat.n_cols = numberOfColumns.
